.DT
query_clothing_maximum_depth
$MUDNAME$ Creator Help
query_clothing_maximum_depth

.SH Name
.SP 5 5
query_clothing_maximum_depth -  This method returns the depth of the clothing type.
.EP

.SH Syntax
.SI 5
int query_clothing_maximum_depth(mixed type)
.EI

.SH Parameters
.SI 5
%^BOLD%^type%^RESET%^ - the type of clothing to check
.EI

.SH Returns
.SI 5
the depth rating of the type
.EI

.SH Defined in
.SI 5
/handlers/clothing_handler.c
.EI

.SH Description
.SP 5 5

This method returns the depth of the clothing type.  The parament
can also be an array, in which case it will return the maximum
non-zero depth.
.EP

.SH See also
.SP 5 5
query_clothing_cannot_remove(), query_clothing_hiding()

.EP

